{"tid":2508940,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「光榮」社長簽名信讚揚《真·三國無双》神還原遊戲、特技迫真","createTime":"2021-04-29T06:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T06:26:06.000Z","uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5c072f01f0e3c21174c15ba9113c37a938957101","tid":2508940,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:17:51.000Z","msg":"【光榮特庫摩社長親筆加持 忠實呈現無双系列「一騎當千」精神】<br />\n<br />\n光榮特庫摩控股株式會社社長襟川陽一更特別以親筆簽名信，稱讚《真&middot;三國無双》片中展示遊戲裏的畫面效果非常逼真，能夠獲得這位創辦人肯定，團隊得悉消息後亦大感鼓舞。<br />\n<br />\n襟川陽一在信中寫道：「電影《真&middot;三國無双》終於要上映很開心，我們事先已觀看全片，看完後覺得很開心，很興奮，很感謝製作團隊的努力。在真人世界裡能表達無双世界的威力真的像作夢一樣，其中幾場戲，把遊戲裡的畫面效果演出得非常逼真，也忠實呈現了無双系列的「一騎當千」精神。現在這部電影要上映了，很期待觀眾的反應，希望觀眾能夠喜歡。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNRzeMVPVjp5DXYZCq8w1sefyZm5iRcZrrozzLCs94zHK?filename=XJNYqfv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJNYqfv.jpg&h=40529f2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0b3ebc64235c93ef6e80a99e459d89fa2a4f6dc","tid":2508940,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"世間甚麼愛叫林雪"},{"pid":"a3012ee1545e911f9c2bf08f5cb884011ce56161","tid":2508940,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0b3ebc64235c93ef6e80a99e459d89fa2a4f6dc","tid":2508940,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:19:05.000Z","msg":"世間甚麼愛叫林雪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f78ecbb9be6aa645456dc6f4556a8fdb65880f","tid":2508940,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"連登仔睇唔睇？"},{"pid":"e61042c4a973daf66b5ad01bba75c7cfcc354ace","tid":2508940,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86f78ecbb9be6aa645456dc6f4556a8fdb65880f","tid":2508940,"uid":23468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"連登仔睇唔睇？"},"citedB